The paper proposes a method for learning normalization operators jointly with low rank matrix factorization, which is a common task in machine learning. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper applies the proposed method to genomics datasets, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.ST (Statistics).
